<section id="canResegment">
    <title>canResegment</title>
    
    <para>Can resegment - indicates whether or not the source text in the scope of the given
            <code>canResegment</code> flag can be reorganized into a different structure of <olink
            targetdoc="../elements/structural/segment.xml" targetptr="segment"
            ><code>segment</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>objects<?oxy_custom_end?>
        within the same parent <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
                ><code>unit</code></olink>.</para>
    <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
        string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis>
        <code>"yes"</code> or <code>"no"</code>.</para>
        
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> default values for this
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string<?oxy_custom_end?>
        depend on the
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        in which the
            <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canResegment"</code>
        property<?oxy_custom_end?> is used:</para>
    
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>When used in <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"
                        ><code>file</code></olink>:</para>
            
            <para>The value <code>"yes"</code>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>When the
                    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>"canResegment"</code>
                property<?oxy_custom_end?> is used in any other
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>:</para>
            <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="canResegment.xml" targetptr="canResegment"
                        ><code>canResegment</code></olink>
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string<?oxy_custom_end?>
                of its parent
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>. </para>   
                
        </listitem>
        
        
        
    </itemizedlist>
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"
            ><code>file</code></olink>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group"
            ><code>group</code></olink>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
            ><code>unit</code></olink>, and <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/segment.xml"
            targetptr="segment"><code>segment</code></olink>. </para>
    
</section>
